793
00:49:55,969 --> 00:49:57,869
This is perfect.

794
00:49:57,871 --> 00:49:59,871
Oh, and, guys,
this is your sound man, Dingo.

795
00:49:59,873 --> 00:50:02,040
Anything you need,
you just let him know.

796
00:50:02,042 --> 00:50:03,976
You got us a sound guy?
