What do we do now?

938
00:57:10,804 --> 00:57:12,570
I don't know.
Give me a second.

939
00:57:12,572 --> 00:57:14,706
There's gotta be
something we can do.

940
00:57:14,708 --> 00:57:16,574
Let me think a second.
